  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis of this study is that mindfulness meditation would decrease the severity of
      obsessive-compulsive symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Before and after 8 weeks of mindfulness program, We will measure Y-BOCS scores in OCD
      patients. As a control program, relaxation and psychoeducation will provided to OCD
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
